values ('itf-f-ch1-l2', 102, 'Systems & Signals', 'Build the lesson around systems as parts working together to produce change, then have the learner classify input and output across personal computers, the human body, and embedded computers. Emphasize that a signal is a message carried in physical form and that actuators are output devices.', '', 'IT Frontiers', 'Beginner', 'itf-f-ch1', 2, 'published', 'guided', true, 'after_attempt', 'encouraging', 'guided', 'lower', '{"course_id": "itf-f", "course_version_id": "itf-f-v1", "lesson_type": "discussion"}'::jsonb)
