values ('itf-f-ch1-l2-s5', 'itf-f-ch1-l2', 'itf-f-ch1-l2-milestone', 5, 'Apply the system model to a microwave', 'reflection', 'practice', 'A microwave oven heats food after a user enters a duration with buttons and dials on its operating panel and presses Start. A turn-tray then rotates while a microwave emitter radiates microwave energy; both stop when the entered duration is reached. Name the three parts mentioned, identify the input device, and identify the two output devices. Explain how the parts work together as one system.', 'text', '', null, '[]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, ARRAY['systems.input', 'systems.process', 'systems.output']::text[], 1, 'reflection', null)
