values ('itf-f-ch1-l4-s5', 'itf-f-ch1-l4', 'itf-f-ch1-l4-milestone', 5, 'Match memory actions to diagrams', 'reflection', 'practice', 'The book gives three diagram descriptions: [1] a copy is sent from storage to main memory; [2] a copy is sent from main memory to storage; [3] main memory is empty while storage still holds signals. Match each situation to diagram 1, 2, or 3: turning off a computer; saving an edited photograph; clicking a photograph thumbnail to see it. Explain why each match follows the rules for main memory and storage.', 'text', '', null, '[]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, ARRAY['memory.storage']::text[], 1, 'reflection', null)
