values ('itf-f-ch2-l1-s3', 'itf-f-ch2-l1', 'itf-f-ch2-l1-milestone', 3, 'Ahmed compares clock rates', 'discussion', 'teach', 'One way to improve performance is to manufacture a CPU with a faster clock rate. In Example 1.3, Ahmed wants a computer that performs better than his old 1 GHz desktop. At the store he compares a laptop with a 3 GHz clock rate and a desktop with a 2 GHz clock rate. He chooses the laptop because its clock rate is fastest in this comparison, so its performance should be better.', 'text', '', null, '[]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, ARRAY['itf.hardware.performance']::text[], 1, 'explanation', null)
