values ('itf-f-ch2-l2-s5', 'itf-f-ch2-l2', 'itf-f-ch2-l2-milestone', 5, 'Compare processor energy', 'reflection', 'practice', 'Make the two processor comparisons from Activities 2.3 and 2.5. With the same number of cores, compare CPUs at 1 GHz, 3 GHz, and 4 GHz: identify which uses the most and least electrical energy and explain why. Then hold the clock rate at 2 GHz and compare single-core, dual-core, and quad-core CPUs: identify which uses the most and least energy and explain why.', 'text', '', null, '[]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, ARRAY['itf.hardware.energy']::text[], 1, 'reflection', null)
