values ('itf-f-ch2-l3-s6', 'itf-f-ch2-l3', 'itf-f-ch2-l3-milestone', 6, 'Compare energy and batteries', 'reflection', 'practice', 'Make the energy and battery comparisons from Activities 3.5 and 3.6. At the same brightness, decide whether the laptop, tablet, or smartphone screen uses the most energy and explain why. For the same desktop screen, decide whether dim, bright, or brightest uses the most and explain why. Then identify which portable type has the largest battery and which has the smallest, explain how battery size affects weight and ease of carrying, and state which type needs a battery that stores more energy and why.', 'text', '', null, '[]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, ARRAY['itf.hardware.portability']::text[], 1, 'reflection', null)
