values ('itf-f-ch3-l1-s3', 'itf-f-ch3-l1', 'itf-f-ch3-l1-milestone', 3, 'Tasks and computer programs', 'discussion', 'teach', 'Instructions occur in sets. Every task has a specific set whose instructions should be performed in order, one after another, until the task is complete. Chen''s morning task begins when he wakes up: brush his teeth, comb his hair, wear his clothes, eat breakfast, and get his school bag. A program is a set of instructions written for a computer, and a computer has programs for the many tasks it must perform. BIOS is one program. Each time a computer is powered on, BIOS checks that its devices are connected and working. Its keyboard-test instructions send an ''Are you OK?'' signal, wait for and receive the keyboard''s reply, write ''KEYBOARD is OK'' to memory, and connect the keyboard to the system.', 'text', '', null, '[]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, ARRAY['logic.sequence', 'itf.software.instructions']::text[], 1, 'explanation', null)
