values ('itf-f-ch3-l3-s4', 'itf-f-ch3-l3', 'itf-f-ch3-l3-milestone', 4, 'Run the failed keyboard branch', 'code', 'practice', 'The keyboard''s signal is ''I am not OK,'' so the BIOS test must follow the No branch. Run the Jargon program and verify that it records the failed status and prints the same kind of error used in the book.', 'code', 'SET device ("KEYBOARD")
SET signal ("I am not OK")
