values ('itf-f-ch4-l1-s5', 'itf-f-ch4-l1', 'itf-f-ch4-l1-milestone', 5, 'Apply files, lists, and tables', 'discussion', 'practice', 'Complete four connected tasks. (1) Liam opens the Word application and then the file "English Essay": identify the instruction file and the data file. (2) Jenna uses the Camera app to take a photo and the Photos app to view it: identify the instruction files and data file. (3) BIOS finds the keyboard and screen connected but the speakers and mouse do not respond: write a Device Status Table with device and status columns. (4) Chen saves "Zoo Trip Essay", "Math Homework", and "Science Homework", then prints "Zoo Trip Essay" and "Zoo Photo 1", "Zoo Photo 2", and "Zoo Photo 5": write separate Files to Save and Files to Print task lists. Label every structure as a list or table.', 'text', '', null, '[]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, ARRAY['itf.data.structures']::text[], 1, 'practice', 'applied')
