values ('itf-f-ch4-l4-s3', 'itf-f-ch4-l4', 'itf-f-ch4-l4-milestone', 3, 'Check final sorted order in Jargon', 'code', 'practice', 'Activities 4.2 and 4.3 sort the book''s name list alphabetically and number list by increasing value. Jargon''s sorted function gives the final order so you can check a hand-worked sequence of comparisons and switches. Run the program and compare its two outputs with those criteria.', 'code', 'SET names (["Cherry", "Kiwi", "Apple", "Banana"])
