values ('itf-f-ch4-l4-s4', 'itf-f-ch4-l4', 'itf-f-ch4-l4-milestone', 4, 'Trace the alphabetical sort', 'discussion', 'practice', 'Trace Activity 4.2 by hand, starting with [Cherry, Kiwi, Apple, Banana]. Compare only consecutive items in the order shown by the book''s pink brackets. After each comparison, write the whole list and state whether a switch occurred. When you reach the end, begin another pass if any switch occurred. Stop only after a complete pass requires no switches, then state the final alphabetical list.', 'text', '', null, '[]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, ARRAY['itf.data.sorting']::text[], 1, 'practice', 'applied')
