values ('itf-f-ch4-l4-s5', 'itf-f-ch4-l4', 'itf-f-ch4-l4-milestone', 5, 'Trace two numerical criteria', 'discussion', 'practice', 'Use the same consecutive-comparison process on [40, 50, 20, 30] twice. First apply Activity 4.3''s criterion of increasing numerical value; then restart from the original list and apply Activity 4.4''s criterion of decreasing numerical value. Show the list after every comparison, mark each switch, repeat passes when needed, and stop each sort only after a full pass has no switches.', 'text', '', null, '[]'::jsonb, '{}'::jsonb, ARRAY['itf.data.sorting']::text[], 1, 'practice', 'applied')
